('9c7cefa9-492b-45ab-ab36-878bcc1d3e4e', '9c6c7ddc-0596-41e5-83b3-b509e8f30b9f', 2, 'Brief on the Decision of the High Court regarding Core Banking Software', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">&nbsp;</span><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">1.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">It may be recalled that the Board in its </span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">69<sup>th</sup> meeting<span style=\"color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">, held on December 04, 2023, has passed the following resolutions:</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; margin: 0in 0in 6pt 0.5in; line-height: 1.5;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">a)<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\"> &nbsp;</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">The Bid of M/S International Consulting Associates (Pvt.) Limited for procurement of Core Banking Solution and Digital Channels is hereby approved as most advantageous Bid at a Total Cost of Rs. 1,761,889,202/- with full scope of the work as defined in RFP as recommended by the Board&rsquo;s IT Committee and the consultant firm KPMG in pursuance of Bank procurement committee.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2; margin: 6.0pt 0in 6.0pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">b)<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\"> &nbsp;</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">Management should issue formal letter of intent/award to M/S International Consulting Associates (Pvt.) Limited as successful bidder for procurement of Core Banking Solution and Digital Channels.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2; margin: 6.0pt 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">c)<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB;\">The decision under agenda item no. 03 taken in its 67<sup>th</sup> meeting is hereby endorsed and the payment terms finalized by the committee (constituted in 66<sup>th</sup> BoD meeting) and the vendor are hereby approved.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 1.5;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">2.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">It may further be called that before implementation of the decision, the Honorable High Court has granted an interim injunction on the procurement process of the Core Banking and hence, implementation of the decision was withheld till vacation of the injunction.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 1.5;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">3.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">In this regard, the Honorable High Court has given its decision dated July 03, 2024, which is attached herewith. Briefing on the matter will be presented during the meeting. </span></p>', 3, NULL, '2024-07-10 09:35:07', '2024-07-10 13:15:00'),
('9c7cf036-b5f9-4d34-840c-aa85b96f2790', '9c6c7ddc-0596-41e5-83b3-b509e8f30b9f', 2, 'Proposed amendment in HR Policies & Procedures Manual', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">1.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\"> &nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">The agenda paper/memorandum received from the Human Resource Management Division regarding the subject noted above is placed before the Board of Directors for consideration and necessary approval.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in 0in .25in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">2.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">It may be noted that the Board Human Resource Committee in its 8<sup>th</sup> meeting held on July 04, 2024, has recommended certain amendments in Human Resource Policies and Procedures Manual for approval of the Board of Directors. These amendments are tabulated in Annex-A, attached herewith.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">3.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><u><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Proposal</span></u></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">The Board is requested to review the proposed amendments in Human Resource Policies and Procedures Manual and pass the following resolution:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">&ldquo;Resolved that the proposed amendments in Human Resource Policies and Procedures Manual, as recommended by the Board Human Resource Committee, are hereby approved.&rdquo;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">&nbsp;</span></p>', 4, NULL, '2024-07-10 09:36:39', '2024-07-10 10:18:38');
