=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">The Board is requested to pass the following resolution:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">&ldquo;Resolved that increase in the Directors&rsquo; Remuneration/ Meeting Fee from Rs.50,000/- to Rs.100,000/- per meeting for Chairman and all Directors, for attending Board and its Committees&rsquo; meetings, is hereby approved with effect from July 01, 2024.&rdquo;</span></p>', 5, NULL, '2024-07-10 09:38:33', '2024-07-11 05:54:11'),
('9c7cf112-0a29-4173-ab1f-ee82b10622bb', '9c6c7ddc-0596-41e5-83b3-b509e8f30b9f', 2, 'Hiring of Management Internees', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">1.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\"> &nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">The agenda paper/memorandum received from the Human Resource Management Division regarding the subject noted above is placed before the Board of Directors for consideration and necessary approval.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">2.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\"> &nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Bank of AJK has been experiencing a prolonged staff shortage and is actively recruiting to ensure seamless banking services for clients. The process of hiring General Banking Officers (GBOs) and Assistants/Cash Sorters through a Testing Services Company is underway, which involves contracting with the Testing Services Company and subsequently recruiting the necessary staff, which is a time-consuming activity. Efforts to hire experienced staff from other banks have also been hindered by various factors, including a lackluster response from the market.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">3.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Recently, BAJK hired the services of Management Interns in order to both train the youth of Azad Jammu &amp; Kashmir and provide financial support to the educated segment of society. Feedback from field functionaries has been positive, and we believe that hiring additional Management Interns will be beneficial for branches, aiding in daily operations until the staff shortage is resolved.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">4.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\"> &nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Thus, considering the comparatively lesser financial impact and encouraging feedback for the Management Interns, approval to hire an additional 50 Management Interns (15 each for Rawalakot, Kotli, and Mirpur Regions <span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">&amp; 05 for Muzaffarabad Region</span>) is being requested with relaxation in age limit from 27 to 35 years and curtailing minimum educational passing marks criteria from 70% to 60% to help mitigate the staff shortage.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">5.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">This agenda was presented in the 8<sup>th</sup> meeting of the Board Human Resource Committee held on July 04, 2024 and after thorough deliberation, the BHRC recommended it for approval of the Board.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">6.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><u><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Proposal</span></u></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: .25in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">The Board is requested to pass the following resolution:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">&ldquo;Resolved that hiring of 50 Management Internees (15 each for Rawalakot, Kotli, and Mirpur Regions <span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Calibri\',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">&amp; 05 for Muzaffarabad Region</span>) are hereby approved with relaxation in age limit from 27 to 35 years and curtailing the minimum educational passing marks criteria from 70% to 60%.&rdquo;</span></p>', 6, NULL, '2024-07-10 09:39:03', '2024-07-12 07:57:57'),
('9c7cf15c-aa7f-47d9-8922-9756b344d578', '9c6c7ddc-0596-41e5-83b3-b509e8f30b9f', 2, 'Confirmation of Resolution Passed Through Circulation', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">1.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">It may be recalled that the Board of Directors had passed the following Resolution through Circulation dated June 07, 2024:</span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin: 0in 0in 0in .25in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 110%; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; color: black;\">&ldquo;Resolved that the Company Secretariat being Registered Office of the Bank of Azad Jammu &amp; Kashmir is hereby established at Kashmir Council Secretariat, F-5/2, F-5 Islamabad. The Company Secretary is hereby relocated to the aforesaid office with immediate effect.&rdquo;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">2.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">The circular resolution passed by the Board at Para 1 above is attached herewith.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">3.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><u><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Proposal</span></u></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">The Board is requested to pass the following resolution:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">&ldquo;Resolved that the Resolution passed by the Board through Circulation, dated June 07, 2024 is hereby recorded and confirmed.&rdquo;</span></p>', 7, NULL, '2024-07-10 09:39:52', '2024-07-10 09:40:10'),
