cing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">The Board is requested to pass the following resolution:</span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">&ldquo;Resolved that the minutes of the Board Subcommittees, circulated to the Board as a part of agenda, are hereby <span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">ratified/ approved</span>.&rdquo;</span></p>', 8, NULL, '2024-07-10 09:42:42', '2024-07-10 09:42:57'),
('9c7cf2ce-7ec8-4842-b7c0-41897c4fce52', '9c6c7ddc-0596-41e5-83b3-b509e8f30b9f', 2, 'Any Other Item(s) with permission of the Chair-Increase in Basic Pay', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">1.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\"> &nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">The agenda paper/memorandum received from the Human Resource Management Division regarding the subject noted above is placed before the Board of Directors for consideration and necessary approval.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">2.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">In the recent budget 2024-25, the Federal Government has granted 25% and 20% increase in the salaries of Government employees of grades 1-16 and 17-22 respectively, enabling them to cope up with the rising inflationary trends in the country. By granting the said increase, it is expected that the general public shall be able to come out of misery and make their both ends meet.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">3.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">The Board of Directors, has already approved grant of 10% &amp; 8% across the board increment to officer and executive cadres respectively and 5% appraisal base increment to the employees of the Bank, incorporated in Human Resource Policies and Procedures Manual approved in 68<sup>th</sup> Board of Directors meeting held on November 13, 2023.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">4.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">During the recent year, the Bank of AJK has performed in an excellent manner and has achieved historical milestones in almost all the KPIs. The Bank has crossed a deposit figure of Rs. 38 Billion and a Profit figure of 927 Million, crossing all the half yearly targets will a great margin. Keeping in view the outstanding performance of the Bank, it is proposed that 10% across the Board increase may please be granted to all the employees of the Bank, enabling them to make their both ends meet in current inflationary scenario of the country. The total financial impact of this increase will be Rs. 22(m) per annum approximately.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">5.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">The agenda regarding above was presented in 9<sup>th</sup> meeting of Board&rsquo;s Human Resource Committee held on July 12, 2024 for deliberation. The BHRC after thorough deliberation recommended Salary Increase @ 10% to all the employees of the Bank across the board for approval of the Board of Directors.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">4.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><u><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Proposal</span></u></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">The Board is requested to pass the following resolution:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">&ldquo;Resolved that increase in basic pay @ 10% to all the employees of the Bank across the board, is hereby approved.&rdquo;</span></p>', 9, NULL, '2024-07-10 09:43:54', '2024-07-12 07:52:02'),
('9cab075c-107e-494c-8482-40f97410064c', '9cab0699-a204-455d-b42f-3256f671b9d6', 2, 'Confirmation of Minutes of 76th Board of Directors’ Meeting', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">1.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">The 76<sup>th</sup> meeting of the Board of Directors was held on <span style=\"color: black;\">July 15, 2024</span>. A copy of the minutes <span style=\"color: black;\">is</span> annexed for the Board&rsquo;s confirmation and approval.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><span style=\"mso-bookmark: _Hlk150275460;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">2.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><u><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Proposal</span></u></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"mso-bookmark: _Hlk150275460;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">The Board is requested to confirm the minutes and pass the following resolution:</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"mso-bookmark: _Hlk150275460;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">&ldquo;Resolved that the minutes of 76<sup>th</sup> meeting of the Board of Directors held on <span style=\"color: black;\">July 12, 2024,&nbsp;</span>are taken as read and confirmed.&rdquo;</span></span></p>', 1, NULL, '2024-08-02 07:29:28', '2024-08-02 07:29:28'),
('9cab07ac-ba87-4d94-b2c1-052fe00a6d33', '9cab0699-a204-455d-b42f-3256f671b9d6', 2, 'Required Course of Action on the Decision of the High Court regarding  Core Banking Software', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">1.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; background: white;\">It may be recalled that</span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"> during previous Board meeting, the Board on the majority voting basis has resolved that:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; background: white; margin: 0in 0in 0in .25in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 110%; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">&ldquo;Notwithstanding that the Board does not avoid to place the Core Banking Software case to the Cabinet but owing to the reason that the process has already been overturned by the High Court and that placing the case to the Cabinet will give impression that the decision is acceptable to the Bank and may could not be challenged in the Supreme Court on sound grounds; thus, on majority voting basis, the matter shall be presented in Supreme Court and a renowned competent lawyer shall be hired to defend the case on behalf of the Bank.&rdquo;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">2.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Thus, following by a thorough deliberation, the Board is requested to unanimously decide on the course of action to be undertaken subsequent to the High Court decision on procurement of Core Banking Software by the Bank of AJK (Annex-A).</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>', 2, NULL, '2024-08-02 07:30:21', '2024-08-02 07:30:21'),
