windowtext;\">Compliance of the Minutes of 76<sup>th</sup> and 77<sup>th</sup> Meetings of the Board of Directors </span></u></strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 317.833px; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0in 5.4pt; height: 0.4in;\" rowspan=\"2\" width=\"214\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: center; text-indent: -1.0pt; line-height: normal;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">The decision was communicated to the relevent division and accordingly, the IT department has started working upon the assignment.</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow: 2; height: 163.55pt;\">\r\n<td style=\"width: 468.625px; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0in 5.4pt; height: 163.55pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"340\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l4 level1 lfo2; background: white;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">a)<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\"> &nbsp;</span></span></span></strong><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><u><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Required Course of Action on the Decision of the High Court regarding Core Banking Software</span></u></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The Board avoiding to incur any additional cost at this moment, agreed that since M/s. KPMG has previously shared a comprehensive report on the Core Banking Software, thus it should be used as a guiding document by the BAJK IT team to furnish a report on financial implications of the project delay or its rebidding. The Board also advised to review the scope and deliverables of the M/s. KPMG to ascertain if they have completed the assignment as per the agreement.</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow: 3; height: 72.4pt;\">\r\n<td style=\"width: 468.625px; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0in 5.4pt; height: 72.4pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"340\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l4 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">b)<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\"> &nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></strong><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><u><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Update on Hiring of Consultancy Services for Raising Regulatory Capital Requirements of Scheduled Bank for BAJK</span></u></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">The Board discussed that since the matter is currently sub-judice, thus Bank should refrain from making any development on the matter till announcement of the Supreme Court decision.</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 317.833px; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0in 5.4pt; height: 72.4pt;\" width=\"214\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: center; line-height: normal;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Noted</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow: 4; height: 72.4pt;\">\r\n<td style=\"width: 468.625px; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0in 5.4pt; height: 72.4pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"340\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l4 level1 lfo2;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">c)<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></strong><!--[endif]--><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><u><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Establishment of BAJK Exchange Company</span></u></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: justify; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 110%; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">The Board was informed that as per telephonic conversation, SBP has scrutinized the documents of BAJK Exchange Company and Fit &amp; Proper Test is under process. </span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 317.833px; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0in 5.4pt; height: 72.4pt;\" width=\"214\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: center; line-height: normal;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">The process of Fit &amp; Proper Test has almost been completed.</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow: 5; height: 72.4pt;\">\r\n<td style=\"width: 140.021px; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-left: 1pt solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; padding: 0in 5.4pt; height: 72.4pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"69\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: normal; tab-stops: 33.8pt;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: SimSun; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">03.</span></strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 468.625px; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0in 5.4pt; height: 72.4pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"340\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; background: white;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><u><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 110%; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Brief on the status of the Appeal filed in Supreme Court of AJK regarding Core Banking Software</span></u></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: justify; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 110%; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">Resolved that the progress made on the appeal filed in Supreme Court of AJK regarding Core Banking Software is hereby recorded.</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 317.833px; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0in 5.4pt; height: 72.4pt;\" width=\"214\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Next date of hearing is September 11, 2024.</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow: 6; height: 72.4pt;\">\r\n<td style=\"width: 140.021px; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-left: 1pt solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; padding: 0in 5.4pt; height: 72.4pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"69\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: normal; tab-stops: 33.8pt;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: SimSun; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">04</span></strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 468.625px; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0in 5.4pt; height: 72.4pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"340\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; background: white;\"><strong><u><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 110%; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Proposed Amendments in Human Resource Policies and Procedures Manual</span></u></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top: 6.0pt; text-align: justify; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 110%; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">Resolved that</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l5 level1 lfo3; background: white; margin: 6.0pt 0in 6.0pt .25in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">a)<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\"> &nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">The proposed amendments in Clause 7.5 of Human Resource Policies and Procedures Manual pertaining to Annual Salary Increase, as recommended by the Board Human Resource Committee, are hereby approved.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l5 level1 lfo3; margin: 0in 0in 0in .25in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">b)<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\"> &nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">The revision in basic pay as envisaged in Clause 7.3, shall be revisited again by the Board Human Resource Committee based on a defined set of criteria, and shall be presented to the Board along with the financial impact and the number of employees in each grade.</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 317.833px; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0in 5.4pt; height: 72.4pt;\" width=\"214\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: center; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo5;\" align=\"center\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">a)<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">The amendments have been incorporated in the Human Resource Policies and Procedures Manual.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo5; margin: 0in 0in 0in .25in;\" align=\"center\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">b)<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">The agenda regarding revision in basic pay, as envisaged in Clause 7.3, will be presented in the forthcoming meeting of the Board HR Committee.</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow: 7; height: 72.4pt;\">\r\n<td style=\"width: 140.021px; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-left: 1pt solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; padding: 0in 5.4pt; height: 72.4pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"69\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: normal; tab-stops: 33.8pt;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: SimSun; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">05</span></strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 468.625px; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0in 5.4pt; height: 72.4pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"340\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6.0pt;\"><strong><u><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Hiring of Management Internees (Batch-2)</span></u></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext;\">Re</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">solved that hiring of 50 Management Internees (15 each for Rawalakot, Kotli and Mirpur Regions, and 05 for Islamic Banking Division) are hereby approved with relaxation in age limit from 27 to 35 years, curtailing minimum educational passing marks criteria from 70% to 60% and retaining salary @ Rs.30,000 per month.</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 317.833px; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0in 5.4pt; height: 72.4pt;\" width=\"214\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: center; line-height: normal;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Advertisement for the positions has been published in newspaper.</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow: 8; height: 22.0pt;\">\r\n<td style=\"width: 140.021px; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-left: 1pt solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; padding: 0in 5.4pt; height: 22pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"69\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: normal; tab-stops: 33.8pt;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: SimSun; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">&nbsp;06.</span></strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 468.625px; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0in 5.4pt; height: 22pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"340\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6.0pt; text-align: justify;\"><strong><u><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Engagement of Testing Firm for Induction of Fresh Staff</span></u></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">Resolved that keeping in view the problem faced by the Bank in hiring of testing firm and to cope with the immediate operational requirement of the Bank, NIBAF Pakistan (established consequent to the merger of IBP and NIBAF), being a sole specialized institute for banking sector in Pakistan and as a wholly-owned subsidiary of SBP mandated with the subject task amongst others, shall be explored for direct contracting under the AJK PPRA Rules for conducting competitive process for induction of MTOs/ GBOs/ BDOs/ Cos/ Tellers in the Bank. In this regard, an opinion of AJK PPRA should be sought if the Bank could engage in direct contracting with the NIBAF Pakistan for conducting tests of the aforesaid positions.</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 317.833px; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0in 5.4pt; height: 22pt;\" width=\"214\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 0in 0in 0in 0.25in; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">&nbsp;AJK PPRA opinion has been sought vide letter dated August 30, 2024.</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow: 9; height: 4.0pt;\">\r\n<td style=\"width: 140.021px; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-left: 1pt solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; padding: 0in 5.4pt; height: 4pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"69\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: normal; tab-stops: 33.8pt;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: SimSun; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">07.</span></strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 468.625px; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0in 5.4pt; height: 4pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"340\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6.0pt; text-align: justify;\"><strong><u><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Islamic Banking Policies and Product Manual</span></u></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top: 6.0pt; text-align: justify; background: white;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 110%; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">Resolved that </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo4; background: white; margin: 6.0pt 0in 6.0pt .25in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">a)<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">The Islamic Banking Policies, Product Manuals and other preliminary Misc items of printed stationery including Account Opening Form, as recommended by the Shariah Board and Management Committee of the Bank, are hereby approved.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo4; background: white; margin: 6.0pt 0in 6.0pt .25in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">b)<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">The tasks of name finalization of the Islamic Bank, its logo and any other relevant work, are hereby referred to the Islamic Banking Committee as already constituted by the Board.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo4; background: white; margin: 6.0pt 0in 6.0pt .25in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">c)</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\"><span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\"> </span></span></span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\"><span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-color-alt: windowtext; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">The Board shall be given a formal presentation on the Islamic Banking Policies and Product Manuals at the earliest.</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 317.833px; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0in 5.4pt; height: 4pt;\" width=\"214\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: center; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo6;\" align=\"center\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">a)<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">The decision was communicated to the relevant division.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: center; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo6;\" align=\"center\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">b)<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">The meeting of the Committee on Islamic Banking will be scheduled soon.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: center; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo6;\" align=\"center\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">c)<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">For presentation on the Islamic Banking Policies and Product Manuals, please refer Agenda No.07</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow: 10; mso-yfti-lastrow: yes; height: 72.4pt;\">\r\n<td style=\"width: 140.021px; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-left: 1pt solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-top: none; padding: 0in 5.4pt; height: 72.4pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"69\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: normal; tab-stops: 33.8pt;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: SimSun; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">09.</span></strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 468.625px; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0in 5.4pt; height: 72.4pt;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"340\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-bottom: 6.0pt; text-align: justify;\"><strong><u><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Other Items-<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span></span></u></strong><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><u><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-no-proof: yes;\">Harassment at Workplace</span></u></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">Resolved that harassment at workplace should be strictly discouraged and the policy in this regard should be followed in true letter and spirit. Such incidents should be instantly reported to the relevant committee, which should take cognizant of the matter, probe the facts and take appropriate action. Confidentiality should be maintained and reporting internal affairs of the Bank to the media, shall be strictly prohibited. Moreover, the details of harassment cases be presented in the next meeting of the Board.</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 317.833px; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0in 5.4pt; height: 72.4pt;\" width=\"214\">\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: normal;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Please refer Agenda No.06</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: 4.5pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -13.5pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span class=\"fontstyle01\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">2.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></strong></span><!--[endif]--><span class=\"fontstyle01\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><u><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: SimSun;\">Proposal</span></u></strong></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: 4.5pt; text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"fontstyle01\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: SimSun;\">The Board is requested to review the compliance report and pass the following resolution:</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0in; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">&ldquo;Resolved that the </span><span class=\"fontstyle01\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: SimSun;\">compliance report of the Management on various decisions taken by the Board of Directors up to its </span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; color: black;\">78<sup>th</sup> meeting held on August</span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"> 12, 2024</span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; color: black;\">, is hereby recorded.&rdquo;</span></p>', 2, NULL, '2024-08-31 19:23:33', '2024-09-01 09:03:47'),
('9ce65e00-7e66-448b-9f1d-964486430c50', '9ce6587d-4dc7-4406-92b6-912aa8726da0', 2, 'Financial Statements for the Half Year, ended June 30, 2024', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',serif; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;</span><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">1.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; color: black;\">The Financial Statements for the Half Year ended June 30, 2024 along with Auditors Letter to the Board, Directors Review Report and agenda paper&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;containing comparative position of Balance Sheet and Profit &amp; Loss Account, received from Financial Control Division, are placed before the Board&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;for its consideration and approval. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in 0in .25in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; color: black; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">2.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; color: black;\">These financial statements are duly reviewed by the Board Audit Committee, which has recommended them for approval of the Board.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">3.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><u><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Proposal</span></u></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">The Board is requested to pass the following resolution as requested by the Financial Control Division:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">\"Resolved that the Financial Statements of the Bank for the <span style=\"color: black;\">half year ended June 30, 2024</span> along with Directors Review Report are hereby approved and waiver for not presenting the same within the prescribed time is also granted.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">Further resolved that Mr. Shahid Shahzad Mir, President/CEO (A), Mr. ______________, Director,</span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"> <span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">Mr. __________________, Director and Mr. ______&shy;&shy;&shy;&shy;____&shy;&shy;&shy;_________, Director are hereby</span> <span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">authorized to sign the Financial Statements for the </span><span style=\"color: black;\">Year ended June 30, 2024</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold;\">.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; color: black;\">Further resolved that instead of publishing in newspaper, the Financial Statements are to be placed on the Bank&rsquo;s website.\"</span></p>', 3, NULL, '2024-08-31 19:25:35', '2024-09-01 06:03:04'),
('9ce65e7c-6dac-4acb-b286-a43993e639dd', '9ce6587d-4dc7-4406-92b6-912aa8726da0', 2, 'Establishment of Staff Training Center at Mirpur', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">1.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\"> &nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">The agenda paper/memorandum received from the Human Resource Management Division regarding the subject noted above is placed before the Board of Directors for consideration and necessary approval.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-no-proof: yes;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">2.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\"> &nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-no-proof: yes;\">It may be noted that the Board Human Resource Committee&nbsp;in its 11<sup>th</sup> meeting held on August 20, 2024 has recommended establishment of Staff Training Centre at Mirpur</span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt;\"> on the </span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-no-proof: yes;\">Government proposed land measuring 5 Kanal at New Mirpur City for the Bank, which will also house residential facilities for the staff of BAJK.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-no-proof: yes;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">3.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">It was proposed that the task of its initiation and organization / management may be assigned to Human Resource Management Division. The responsibilities of Staff Training College were proposed to be as under:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo3; margin: 0in 0in 6.0pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-no-proof: yes;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">a)<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Arranging in house training programs for the staff in the following banking disciplines through maximum use of internal resources.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.5in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo2; margin: 0in 0in 0in 1.0in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">I.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Laws relating to banking.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.5in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo2; margin: 0in 0in 0in 1.0in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">II.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Bank&rsquo;s Operations and Internal Controls.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.5in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo2; margin: 0in 0in 0in 1.0in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">III.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Credit initiation processing, approval and disbursement.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.5in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo2; margin: 0in 0in 0in 1.0in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">IV.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Training in Credit Administration.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.5in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo2; margin: 0in 0in 0in 1.0in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">V.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">SBP Prudential Regulations as applicable in the Bank.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.5in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo2; margin: 0in 0in 0in 1.0in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">VI.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">IT and Core Banking Software.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-add-space: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.5in; line-height: normal; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo2; margin: 0in 0in 0in 1.0in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">VII.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Training in Soft Skills like Leadership traits, Time &amp; Stress Management, Service Quality etc.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: 1; margin: 0in 0in 0in 1in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">VIII.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Branch Profitability Planning.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.5in; margin: 0in 0in 0in 1in; line-height: 1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">IX.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Training in New liability / asset Products as and when launched by the Bank.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left: 1in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.5in; line-height: 1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">X.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Any other training deemed important by the Management. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo3; margin: 0in 0in 6.0pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-no-proof: yes;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">b)<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">The Staff Training College may also derive support and expertise from external banking and management experts within resource constraints and with the approval of the competent authority.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo3; margin: 0in 0in 6.0pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-no-proof: yes;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">c)<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">The Staff Training College will keep close liaison with all the Divisions at Head Office and Regional Heads to get benefits from their valuable inputs, suggestions and feedback.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .5in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo3;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-no-proof: yes;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">d)<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">The Staff Training College on its own will also carry assessment of the level of expertise of the staff in their assigned tasks through study of internal / external Audit reports. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">4.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><u><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Proposal</span></u></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">The Board is requested to pass the following resolution:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">&ldquo;Resolved that the proposal for establishment of Staff Training Centre at Mirpur, as recommended by the Board Human Resource Committee, is hereby approved.&rdquo;</span></p>', 4, NULL, '2024-08-31 19:26:56', '2024-09-01 08:04:49');
INSERT INTO `agenda_items` (`id`, `meeting_id`, `user_id`, `title`, `description`, `order`, `deleted_at`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
('9ce65ea6-26ab-42b5-8b50-9139482f9e49', '9ce6587d-4dc7-4406-92b6-912aa8726da0', 2, 'Talent Pool Scheme 2024', '<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">1.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\"> &nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">The agenda paper/memorandum received from the Human Resource Management Division regarding the subject noted above is placed before the Board of Directors for consideration and necessary approval.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">2.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-no-proof: yes;\">The effective Human Resource Management involves career planning, development and succession planning, where progressive organizations strive to acquire and retain talented employees to ensure quality, cost-consciousness and productivity for future growth and sustainability. Keeping in view the aforesaid, the Board Human Resource Committee in its 11<sup>th</sup> meeting held on August 20, 2024 was proposed that it would be appropriate to identify and nurture a pool of talented employees, from both regular and contractual staff up to OG-II Grade, through a competitive selection process, to help them grow to their full potential and assume key positions, ultimately enabling the HRMD to implement best HR practices that drive the bank\'s competitive edge.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">3.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">As proposed to the Board HR Committee, the following monitory and career enriching benefits shall accrue to the members of talent pool:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;a)<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">10% salary rise in basic pay (For both Permanent &amp; Contractual employees)</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;b)<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Elevation in next higher-grade maximum one step above, subject to availability of vacancy, in case of Permanent employee and regularization of&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; service in case of contractual employees.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;c)<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Preference for posting on leadership positions</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-bottom: 10pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;d)<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">Continuous professional learning and grooming through in house and external training programs.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\">However, on becoming member of talent pool it will be necessary to achieve/maintain performance rating A or B in annual appraisals to retain this membership in future.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\" style=\"margin-left: .25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -.25in; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">4.<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bi